                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>For each month, the miracles include the following ʾarke-hymns:</note>
                     <note>I-1) እንበለ፡ ሕማም፡ አምላክ፡ አመ፡ ከመ፡ ዮም። ... (<locus from="15va" to="16ra">15va-16ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-2) ኦዘሐወጽኮሙ፡ ለደቂቀ፡ ሥርዓት፡ ሠለስቱ። ... (<locus target="24ra">24ra-</locus>va)</note>
                     <note>I-3) ኦዘረዳእኮ፡ ለቴዎድሮስ፡ መዋዒ። ... (<locus target="34va">34va-</locus>vb)</note>
                     <note>I-4) ኦዘወሀብኮ፡ እምአፈ፡ በላዒ፡ መብልዓ። ... (<locus from="39vb" to="40rb">39vb-40rb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-5) ኦዘተዘለፍኮ፡ ለበለዓም፡ ውስተ፡ ፍኖቱ። ... (<locus target="56rb">56rb-</locus>va)</note>
                     <note>I-6) ኦዘባላሕኮሙ፡ በወርኃ፡ ሚያዝያ፡ ባልሆ። ... (<locus target="64ra">64ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-7) ኦእንተ፡ ፆርከ፡ በክሳድ፡ አኃዜ። ... (<locus target="68vb">68vb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-8) ኦዘአጽናእከ፡ እም፡ ኃጕለ፡ ድቀት፡ ወትንታኔ። ... (<locus target="86vb">86vb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-9) ኦዘቀተልኮ፡ ለሰናክሬም፡ ጸአሌ። ፈጣሬ።... (<locus from="94vb" to="95ra">94vb-95ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-10) ኦዘአጽናእኮ፡ ለቍስጣንጢኖስ፡ ኃሣሤ። ... (<locus target="104ra">104ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>I-11) ኦዘፈወስኮ፡ ለሕዝቅያስ፡ እምደዊሁ። ... (<locus target="11">11</locus>
                        <ref type="mss" corresp="ES0vb111">0vb-111</ref>ra)</note>
                     <note>I-12) ኦዘኃደጎ፡ ለዘኃደጎ፡ መንፈሱ። ወዳዊትሃ፡ ዓቀብከ። ... (<locus target="118rb">118rb</locus>).</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                         
                        <locus target="119va">119va</locus>: This book was written in the time of Säbʾa Gadǝs and <roleName type="title">qes gabaz</roleName> Kidāna Dǝngǝl. The one who purchased it is ʿabeto Walda Gärima with 12 ʾAläba.The one who stole this book or erased it...
 
                        
                     </colophon>
